The paper discusses the security and information leakage rate in wireless communication systems, which falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also proposes an approximation for the average information leakage rate, which involves optimization of transmission rates, indicating the involvement of networked systems (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY).
